## Summary
This documentation explains how to effectively use Amplitude's funnel analysis to track user flows, identify critical conversion paths, and improve conversion rates. It covers identifying appropriate funnel events, designing funnels with proper event ordering and conversion windows, building and comparing funnels across user cohorts, and taking action on insights through targeted messaging to users who drop off at key points.

